overview: US marshal Lawlor (Starrett) takes on a gang of cattle rustlers headed by Taylor (Dick Curtis). His reasons are partly personal: Conway (Edward LeSaint), the cattle-baron father of Lawlor's sweetheart Madge (Meredith), has been murdered by Taylor's minions.
tagline: RHYTHMS RING AS GUNS BLAZE AND THRILLS THUNDER!
title: West of the Santa Fe
